## premultiply variable

Multiplies RGB channels w/ alpha channel. Assumes alpha is in last vector component and \[0..1\] interval. Does NOT clamp result.

<b>Signature:</b>

```typescript
premultiply: (out: Color | null, src: import("@thi.ng/api").ArrayLikeIterable<number>) => Color
```
